author: Daniel Greene
description:
Have you been in a reading slump? Or maybe books just don't hit like they used to? Whether it's burnout, distraction, or just life getting in the way—this video is for you. I'm breaking down how to actually enjoy reading again, rebuild the habit, and rediscover the magic that made you fall in love with stories in the first place.

📚 Favorite recommendations, mindset shifts, and methods that helped me personally
🧠 Whether you're a lapsed bookworm or just burned out on epic sagas
❤️ No guilt, no pressure—just practical ways to reconnect with your love of reading
